# US runtime state — must not be tracked. A pre-commit stash hitting the
# .venv interpreter lock on 2026-04-21 left us/lab/state/forward/ partially
# reverted to HEAD because these files were tracked instead of ignored.
# PIPELINE_ORCHESTRATOR.md logs the same class of incident on 2026-04-20.
# Everything under us/lab/state/ and us/lab/jobs/ is regenerated by the
# EOD runner; repo should carry code, not per-run output.
us/lab/state/
us/lab/jobs/

backup/db/*.dump
*.dump
